 static block:
------------------
-> static block is exceuted only 1 time , during class loading
-> static block contains code ; code only for initializing the static variables.
-> static block is exceuted before the constr.
  

syntax:
static{
  
  
  
}


instance varibles + instace method + constr   ---> 1 set
(sepcifc data)        ( any logic)     ( initialzing the i.v. when obj is created)

static varibles + static methods + static block ---> 1 set
(common data)      ( logic for s.v.)  ( intilizing the s.v. during class loading)